## Making the badge Arduino shield compatible

To make the badge Arduino shield compatible you'll need to solder simple strips of header pins onto the back of the badge. You need the following headers [^1]

| Qty | Type | Use | Rapid part |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | 2x03 Male | SPI | |
| 2 | 1x08 Female | Power, Analog pins | |
| 2 | 1x10 Female | Digital pins | |
| 1 | 2x08 Male | Ethernet | |

